{
  "_ILLUSTRATIVE_ONLY" : "This file is a reference sample for docs/05-runbook-multi-org.md. It is NOT part of the LicenseManager package (it lives under docs/, outside force-app/), it is NOT deployable, and 'ORG_B_CONNECTION_PLACEHOLDER' is not a real CRM Analytics connection. It shows only the 2-org shape (load -> stamp SourceOrg -> append -> save) applied to the LM_ProductLicense__c branch of the purchase-utilization dataset. See docs/samples/README.md.",
  "version" : "67.0",
  "nodes" : {
